OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780733118
OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,FThe UK still does not have a "grip" on
OL,7,Fhow to manage asylum and has no long-
OL,8,Fterm plan for how to accommodate
OL,9,Fpeople when they arrive in the
OL,10,Fcountry, a new report has found.
OL,12,FThe Home Office is too focused on
OL,13,Fshort-term fixes, and, in a "shocking
OL,14,Fand unacceptable state of affairs",
OL,15,Fdoes not effectively keep track of
OL,16,Fwhere those with failed asylum claims
OL,17,Fhave gone, the Public Accounts
OL,18,FCommittee (PAC) said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
