PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780733118
OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,FIt noted that the allocation of
OL,7,Fresources across the asylum system was
OL,8,Foften "fragmented and often reactive",
OL,9,Fleading to backlogs being repeatedly
OL,10,Fshifted rather than reduced.
OL,12,FSir Geoffrey Clifton-Brown, chairman
OL,13,Fof the committee, said the report
OL,14,Fpainted a "disturbing picture", noting
OL,15,Fthat control of the UK's asylum system
OL,16,F"had been all but lost" at the time of
OL,17,Fthe inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
