OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780733118
OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"The focus on short term, reactive
OL,12,F'fixes' has left the government
OL,13,Fchasing after pressures pushed from
OL,14,Fone part of the system to the next,"
OL,15,FClifton-Brown said.
OL,17,F"There is no clear strategy uniting
OL,18,Fthese efforts, and engagement across
OL,19,Fdepartments and with local authorities
OL,20,Fis patchy at best.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
