OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1780733118
OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,F"Given senior officials' inability to
OL,7,Farticulate what the asylum system is
OL,8,Fcollectively trying to achieve, it is
OL,9,Fno wonder such a directionless
OL,10,Fbureaucracy ends with people at the
OL,11,Fheart of it either left in limbo, or
OL,12,Flost entirely."
OL,14,FThe Home Office told the committee
OL,15,Fwhile it knows where "vast majority"
OL,16,Fof failed asylum seekers are, it does
OL,17,F"not count absolutely everybody out of
OL,18,Fthe country".
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@VOUwD@dO]
