OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,F"The system of monitoring failed
OL,7,Fasylum seekers needs a complete
OL,8,Foverhaul," the report adds.
OL,10,FLabour has vowed to end the use of
OL,11,Fasylum hotels by the end of the
OL,12,Fcurrent Parliament, but the committee
OL,13,Fsaid past attempts to use alternative
OL,14,Fsites have proved difficult.
OL,16,FCharities supporting asylum seekers in
OL,17,Fthe UK said they hoped the report
OL,18,Fwould push the government to rethink
OL,19,Fplans for refugees to undertake
OL,20,Freviews of their status every 30
OL,21,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
