OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,F"The Committee is right on the need
OL,7,Ffor better decisions to reduce the
OL,8,Fneed for appeals," Imran Hussain,
OL,9,FDirector of External Affairs at the
OL,10,FRefugee Council, said. Poor quality
OL,11,Fasylum decisions simply create a
OL,12,Fbacklog of people waiting to appeal.
OL,14,F"Getting decisions right first time
OL,15,Fwould reduce backlogs and help end the
OL,16,Fuse of expensive hotels, which fuel
OL,17,Fcommunity tensions and leave men,
OL,18,Fwomen and children trapped in limbo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
