OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,F"Britain needs a fair, controlled and
OL,7,Fhumane asylum system that processes
OL,8,Fapplications quickly and fairly.
OL,10,F"That way, refugees who have the right
OL,11,Fto stay can integrate and contribute
OL,12,Fto the communities that welcome them,
OL,13,Fwhile those found not to be refugees
OL,14,Fcan be returned with dignity and
OL,15,Frespect."
