OL,3,CUK's asylum system in need of
OL,4,C'complete overhaul', report finds
OL,6,FResponding to the report, a Home
OL,7,FOffice spokesperson said: "Asylum
OL,8,Fclaims are down, hotel use is falling
OL,9,Fand immigration enforcement activity
OL,10,Fis at the highest level on record `
OL,11,Fwith the largest number of raids and
OL,12,Farrests ever.
OL,14,F"We've tracked down and removed nearly
OL,15,F70,000 illegal migrants and foreign
OL,16,Fcriminals since the government took
OL,17,Foffice ` a 41% increase.
OL,19,F"Any asylum seekers who break their
OL,20,Fbail conditions by absconding will be
OL,21,Ftracked down and arrested."
